## Month 2: Master LLM App Development

**Goal:** Build real AI-powered applications using the OpenAI and Anthropic APIs. Write prompts that work reliably, get structured data out of models, make them call your functions, and handle everything that can go wrong.

---

### 1. Prompting Fundamentals

Prompting is the craft of writing instructions that produce consistent, reliable outputs from models that are fundamentally probabilistic.

| Resource | Link | Notes |
