### 3. Function / Tool Calling

Tool calling transforms an LLM from a text generator into something that can take actions — search the web, query a database, call your API, run code.

> **How it works:** The model doesn't execute your functions. It returns a structured call with the function name and arguments. Your code then executes the call and sends the result back.

