| DeepEval | [Link](https://deepeval.com/docs/getting-started) | Open-source, pytest-inspired. 50+ built-in metrics. |
| Promptfoo | [Link](https://github.com/promptfoo/promptfoo) | CLI for testing and evaluating LLM apps. CI/CD integration. |
| LangSmith | [Link](https://smith.langchain.com/) | Tracing, debugging, and evaluation for LangChain/LangGraph. |
| Ragas | [Link](https://docs.ragas.io/) | Specialized for RAG pipelines. Measures faithfulness, relevancy, precision, recall. |

> **Critical mindset:** Every prompt change, model swap, or retrieval tweak you make without running evals is a gamble. The engineers who ship reliable AI products run evals constantly.

